What is Request Logging Middleware?/How do you log HTTP requests in ASP.NET Core using middleware?
Request Logging Middleware is a custom ASP.NET Core middleware used to log incoming HTTP requests and outgoing responses, including request path, method, status code, and execution time.

Middleware যা প্রতিটি HTTP request এবং response log করে।

Example log:

Request: GET /api/test
Response Status: 200
Execution Time: 120 ms

Flow:

Client Request
      ↓
Request Logging Middleware
      ↓
Controller
      ↓
Response
